! style="background:#ffdead;"|Binocular field
! style="background:#ffdead;"|Combined field{{-}}(binocular + periphery)
|-
!  style="background:#efefef; text-align:center;"| Lemurs
| 10<U+2013>15<U+00B0>
| 114<U+2013>130<U+00B0>
| 250<U+2013>280<U+00B0>
